充足理據 係合理 有邏輯<br />\n<br />\n有啲說話講左就唔可以打倒自己<br />\n<br />\n例如你支持獨立 就唔會退去 建設民主中國<br />\n<br />\n例如你支持自決 因為入唔到閘 就加入返自己一開頭唔想入既傳媒泛民政黨 係唔得<br />\n<br />\n咁即係你只係為9萬6 <br />\n<br />\n連人地監察你每月捐款 都比劉小麗講到係抹黑 打壓你咁款 <br />\n<br />\n咁呢啲人就係政棍 開口頭承諾 同平常泛民入到去逗人工 票又唔投 冇乜分別"},{"pid":"c7584600dbee54df4096576c3cf1b03eef21dbab","tid":721444,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c42cf2a7d92081efff2e56bf3e2c70a1ddca27ef","tid":721444,"uid":33890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:13:04.000Z","msg":"我記得佢當年成日單單打打D傳統政黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:42:01.000Z","msg":"唔係點做到非建制最高票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024c552418768d5f9b63c652cd9598a76280f699","tid":721444,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:50:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解佢唔加入本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為本土派冇撚用囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"563dc5fb1719c87bc571303c8b241e5e89768f9f","tid":721444,"uid":65774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"024c552418768d5f9b63c652cd9598a76280f699","tid":721444,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:50:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解佢唔加入本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為本土派冇撚用囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:53:35.000Z","msg":"講到飯民好撚有用咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hk